{"Sid":0,"Did":18095,"Id":"282722","Title":"蘇澳蜃市","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-23/136de59c-3fc7-44a2-9c80-dc0b51bb2530/collection/3046b186-ad27-401e-928e-0e0b7eaff3bd/108-sea-cw-744-201911081335345dc4f9e072b6d0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n西元1825(道光五)年，烏竹芳就任噶瑪蘭第十三任通判，有感於這片土地山海靈異，景物秀麗，遂選定蘭陽八景，特標其名、而誌其勝，並且為每一景觀寫下一首七言絕句，”蘇澳蜃市”即為其一。「澳水回旋地角東，山光日色照瞳矓。蜃樓海市何人見，遙在澹烟疏雨中。」蘇澳港三面環山，北方澳和南方澳迴旋環拱形成天然港澳。春夏之際，澹煙疏雨，港內海面風平浪靜，山光與日色微明，光線在空氣中透過折射將遠處的景物倒影入海，幻為樓閣，宛如仙境一般。遂有”蘇澳蜃市”美麗讚稱。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.8533264","Keyword_Latitude":"24.594229","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/E223B445-1BEA-4FAF-A84C-324DF17427B2","Original_Identifier":"282722","Keyword_Subject_1":"生物、生態與環境","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"烏竹芳 / 蘇澳港 / 蘭陽八景","dates":"創作時間 / 清朝道光年間/臺灣的清領時期","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/23 20:54:21","Creator":"烏竹芳","publisher":"","mediaType":"照片","language":"","timelines":"","city":"宜蘭縣蘇澳鎮","address":"不詳","lng":"121.8533264","lat":"24.594229","contributors":"","contributor":"莊文生;鐘碧娟;謝淑娟","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-23/136de59c-3fc7-44a2-9c80-dc0b51bb2530/collectionOpen/0efdeb2f-ed10-4fae-be01-a7cfd70161c3/108-sea-cw-744-re-201911081336595dc4f9e072b6d0.jpg"}}